                </div>
                <div class="skills-category">
                    <h3>Databases:</h3>
                    <p>MySQL, SQLite, MongoDB</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skills-category">
                    <h3>Tools & Platforms:</h3>
                    <p>WordPress, Android Studio, Git, GitHub, Jira, n8n Automation, Figma</p>
                </div>
                <div class="skills-category">
                    <h3>Other Skills:</h3>
                    <p>UI/UX Design, Web Scraping, API Integration, Automation Workflows, AI/ML Basics</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="experience">
                <h2>Professional Experience</h2>
                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3>WordPress Developer</h3>
                    <p><strong>Aspiration Softech</strong> | 6 Months</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Developed responsive and SEO-optimized WordPress websites</li>
                        <li>Customized themes and plugins to meet client requirements</li>
                        <li>Implemented custom UI designs and learned LMS and e-commerce systems</li>
                        <li>Gained hands-on experience with real client projects</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="experience-item">
                    <h3>Python Developer Intern</h3>
                    <p><strong>Cognifyz Technologies</strong> | 1 Month</p>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Completed multiple Python-based tasks and mini projects</li>
                        <li>Developed a small game using Python</li>
                        <li>Learned and implemented basic web scraping techniques</li>
                        <li>Gained exposure to practical software development workflows</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="projects">
                <h2>Projects</h2>
                <div class="project-item">
                    <h3>QuickTrade Marketplace</h3>
                    <a href="https://github.com/your-github-profile/quicktrade" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                    <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Python, Django, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, SQL</p>
                    <p>OLX-like marketplace where users can buy and sell products. Features include user authentication, product search and filters, chat system, advertisement auto-expiry, profile management, and ad editing. Custom admin panel and fully mobile-responsive design.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-item">
                    <h3>MobHub - Mobile Phone Store</h3>
                    <a href="https://github.com/your-github-profile/mobhub" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                    <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Python, Django, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap, SQL</p>
                    <p>E-commerce platform for purchasing mobile phones. Product listing, category-based browsing, and user authentication.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-item">
                    <h3>Wrist Gem - Watch Selling Website</h3>
                    <a href="https://github.com/your-github-profile/wristgem" target="_blank">GitHub</a>
                    <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Laravel, PHP, SQL, HTML, CSS, JavaScript, Bootstrap</p>
                    <p>Online watch store with login/logout and checkout system. Admin-side product and order management.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-item">
                    <h3>Save for Later - Bookmark Android App</h3>
                    <p><strong>Technologies:</strong> Android Studio, Kotlin, Firebase</p>
                    <p>Android app to save and manage bookmarks. Automatically identifies tags from pasted links. Categorizes bookmarks intelligently for better organization.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="project-item">
                    <h3>Automation Projects</h3>
                    <p>Built an n8n automation that analyzes job posts received on Telegram and automatically applies for jobs via email or WhatsApp.</p>
                    <p>Developed an automation to manage GitHub repositories by committing a small daily task automatically to maintain consistency.</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="certifications">
                <h2>Certifications</h2>
                <div class="certification-item">
                    <h3>Google UX Design Professional Certificate</h3>
                    <p>Google (Coursera) | November 2024</p>
                    <p>Foundations of UX Design, UX Research and Testing, Wireframing and Prototyping, High-Fidelity Design in Figma, UI Design for Websites, UX Design for Social Good</p>
                </div>
                <div class="certification-item">
                    <h3>Automate Tasks and Processes with Jira</h3>
                    <p>Coursera Project Network | 2025 | Grade: 100%</p>
                </div>
                <div class="certification-item">
                    <h3>Fake News Detection with Machine Learning</h3>
                    <p>Coursera Project Network | 2025 | Grade: 83%</p>
                </div>
            </section>

            <section id="languages">
                <h2>Languages</h2>
                <p>English, Hindi, Gujarati</p>
            </section>

            <section id="contact">
                <h2>Contact</h2>
                <p>Feel free to reach out to me!</p>
                <form id="contact-form">
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="name">Name:</label>
                        <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="email">Email:</label>
                        <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="form-group">
                        <label for="message">Message:</label>
                        <textarea id="message" name="message" rows="5" required></textarea>
                    </div>
                    <button type="submit" class="retro-button">Send Message</button>
                </form>
            </section>
        </main>

        <footer>
            <p>© 2023 Anas Mansuri. All rights reserved.</p>
        </footer>
    </div>

    <script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
